name: Oh_Home_Chester_6-piece_Dining_Set
description: The Chester 6-piece dining set includes a table, four chairs and a bench. The large spacious tabletop offers ample food and elbow room and seating space for many. Thick, sturdy legs in an X-design complete the piece. The side chairs feature traditional straight lines and simplistic chair backs. A luxurious tan fabric covers a plush seat.
